onferencia</a></li></ul><p><a id="References" name="References"></a></p><h2>References</h2><ol class="references"><li id="cite_note-0"><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">↑</a> Pogrebinschi, Thamy, Moving away from liberal democracy: Participation, representation, and political experimentalism in Brazil (2010). Paper delivered at the Ash Center Democracy Seminar, Harvard Kennedy School, on September 8, 2010, p.2.</li><li id="cite_note-1"><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">↑</a> Pogrebinschi, Thamy and Fabiano Santos. (2010). “Entre Representação e Participação: As conferências nacionais e o experimentalismo democrático brasileiro”. Série Pensando o Direito. Ministério da Justiça, Brasília, p.43.</li><li id="cite_note-2"><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">↑</a> These are the national conferences that possessed a: a) deliberative, b) normative and c) national character, according to Pogrebinschi’s research on the national conferences (2010): Pogrebinschi, Thamy and Fabiano Santos. “Entre a Representação e Participação: As conferências nacionais e o experimentalismo democrático brasileiro”. Instituto Universitário de Pesquisas do Rio de Janeiro (IUPERJ), p.31.</li><li id="cite_note-3"><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">↑</a> Pogrebinschi, Thamy, Moving away from liberal democracy: Participation, representation, and political experimentalism in Brazil (2010). Paper delivered at the Ash Center Democracy Seminar, Harvard Kennedy School, on September 8, 2010, p.23.</li><li id="cite_note-4"><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">↑</a> Pogrebinschi, Thamy and Fabiano Santos. (2010). Relatório Final da Pesquisa “Entre a Representação e Participação: As conferências nacionais e o experimentalismo democrático brasileiro”. Série Pensando o Direito.Ministério da Justiça, Brasília, p.43.</li><li id="cite_note-5"><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">↑</a> Pogrebinschi, Thamy, Moving away from liberal democracy: Participation, representation, and political experimentalism in Brazil (2010). Paper delivered at the 