      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-demographics-target field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Participants (Demographics):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_demographics_target%3A112">General Public</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-public-roles-target field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Participants (Public Roles):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A128">Lay Public</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A129">Stakeholder Organizations (e.g. NGOs, Neighbourhood Associations, Industry Representatives)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A131">Elected Public Official</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-participant-selection field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Recruitment:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_participant_selection%3A33">Open to all</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_participant_selection%3A127">Appointment</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-process field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Process</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-methods field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Methods:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/methods/citizen-conferences">Citizen Conferences</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitated field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facilitation?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Yes</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If yes, were they ...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_facilitation_type%3A171">Peer Facilitators (i.e. other participants not professional facilitators)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-method field-type-list-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facetoface, Online or Both:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Face-to-Face</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-communication-mode field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Interaction among Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A9">Discussion, Dialogue, or Deliberation</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A135">Express opinions/preferences only</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A137">Formal Testimony</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Decision Method(s)?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class=